Industry Perspective · Case Study

@region main
# From Industry Signal to Strategic Analysis

A LinkedIn post became a professional industry analysis in under an hour.

A simple ranking of the largest FPSO projects became a structured examination of:

- project scope
- CAPEX comparability
- development status
- omitted projects
- ownership models
- phased versus integrated development
- and the strategic assumptions hidden inside the ranking

@region caption
The input was a LinkedIn post. The output was an industry perspective.

